* CORNWALL CAPITAL SAYS INSTITUTIONAL SHAREHOLDER SERVICES RECOMMENDED KEWEENAW SHAREHOLDERS VOTE WHITE PROXY CARD FOR ELECTION OF CORNWALL’S NOMINEES Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
